points.description:
Meet at car park of the Barley Mow ph in Witnesham.
Optional lunch afterwards
Meet at car park of Recreation Ground. Turn down drive opposite FP sign [big new house on corner] at Ipswich end of village.
Meet at large lay-by outside Wolves View on right hand side of B1071, Ipswich to Hadleigh road; approx. 1 mile beyond Wolves Wood RSPB Reserve and 600 yds before roundabout.
Meet at car park of YM Rugby Club in The Street at Rushmere St Andrew; approx 100 yds from church
Meet at car park of Newbourne village hall; approx. 400yds from The Fox ph
Meet at car park of Henley Community Centre. At x-roads in village, turn up beside the garge and car park is opposite the shurch.
Meet at car park of Suffolk Wildlife HQ in Ashbocking which is signosted approx. 600yds on your left after B1077/B1078 x-roads. going N from Ipswich.
Meet at car park of Stutton Community Centre; approx. 1 mile from main entrance to Alton Water on B1080 coming from Royal Hospital School.

Meet at parking area at end of Woodbridge Airfield runway.  Follow signs for rendlesham Forest Centre from Wilford Bridge roundabout on B1084. Turn right for Centre and parking is 100 yds beyond Holly House on you right.
Meet at car park of Hintlesham & Chattisham Community Centre, opposite the bhuch on the main road through Hintlesham.
Meet at car park of Iken Cliff picnic area.
Meet at car park of Alder Carr Farm Shop
Meet at car park of Pinewood Community Centre in Laburnam Close, Ipswich at the back of ONE sixth form college.

Meet at parking area at the end of Woodbridge airfield runway. Follow brown signs for Rendlesham Forest Centre from Wilford Bridge roundabout on B1084. Parking is 200 yds beyond Holly House on your right.
Meet at car park of Hintlesham & Chattisham Community Centre opposite the church in Hintlesham
Meet at car park of Shotley Community Centre on the right of B1456 near The Rose ph.
Meet at car park of Otley village hall in Chapel Road.
Meet at car park of Brantham Leisure Centre
Meet at car park of Debenham Leisure Centre
Meet at parking area opposite the church on Snape x-roads [jcn.A1094/B1069]
Meet at overflow car park of Wyevale garden Centre, off roundabout on A12 near Woodbridge
Meet on the green infront of Thorpeness Meare boathouse.

Meet at car park at Sutton Heath [SOUTH] picnic site.  Take B1083 from Wilford bridge roundabout towards Bawdsey. Pass Sutton Hoo and after approx. 1.5 miles on sharp right hand bens is car park on your left.
Meet at private car park of Admirals Plastic's opposite the Shepherd & Dog ph. and near Suffolk Showground.
Meet at car park of Melton Riverside picinic site, just over the level crossing at Melford station.
